lemma proj_dual\<^sub>l\<^sub>s\<^sub>s\<^sub>t: "proj l (dual\<^sub>l\<^sub>s\<^sub>s\<^sub>t A) = dual\<^sub>l\<^sub>s\<^sub>s\<^sub>t (proj l A)"
proof (induction A)
case (Cons a A)
obtain l b where a: "a = (l,b)"
by fastforce
thus?case
using Cons
unfolding unlabel_def proj_def
by (cases b) auto
qed simp
